{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","title":"progress","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgress":{"abstract":[{"text":"A structure containing information about an offline pack’s current download","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"progress.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogress","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/progress":{"fragments":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"progress","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/